  "title": "Tool Maker #74912",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Tool Maker</strong></li><li>Working Location: Ubi</li><li>Working Hours: 6 days (Mon – Sat, 8.00am – 4.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + OT + Performance bonus (Quarterly)</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assemble, troubleshoot, take apart, and create new plastic moulds.</li><li>Attend mould testing and optimize the moulding process for consistent quality.</li><li>Perform mould repair, maintenance, and troubleshoot moulding issues; keep records.</li><li>Inspect all mould components and workpieces.</li><li>Interpret engineering drawings and understand manufacturing processes and measurement.</li><li>Assemble and debug new tools to ensure timely submission.</li><li>Keep the work area and equipment clean.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or NITEC in Precision Engineering or related fields.</li><li>Experience in mould setting and tool design.</li><li>Strong analytical and problem-solving abilities.</li><li>Excellent communication and teamwork skills.</li><li>Able to work independently and as part of a team.</li><li>Experience operating different types of moulding machines.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#74912 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
